I"÷<p>John feels funny about Christmas carols, Roger moves to Canada, Esther writes mandatory letters from camp, and much more. Recorded live in Toronto at the Bloor Hot Docs Cinema as part of the inaugural <a href="http://www.hotdocs.ca/p/podcastfestival">Hot Docs Podcast Festival</a>.</p>

